title: Example Publication
text:
Welcome
This HTML book is an example of publications by the IU Libraries’ Scholarly Communications Department Non-Traditional Literature Publishing Service.
If you want to pubish non-traditional literature via our service, please contact Adam Mazel, Digital Publishing Librarian at amazel@iu.edu.
